    <h3>Why does Poppy look like that?</h3>
    <br>
    <p>Poppy is actually in the process of solving complex mathematical equations at all times.</p>
    <br>
    <h3>What is Poppy's favorite color?</h3>
    <br>
    <p>Poppy is a cat which means she can only see in greens and blues. Her favorite color is purple. 
    </p>
    <br>
    <h3>What are Poppy's favorite activities?</h3>
    <br>
    <p>Poppy likes a lot of activities like playing with toys, knocking stuff off of counters, and getting in the way.</p>
    <br>
    <h3>What kind of breed is Poppy?</h3>
    <br>
    <p>Poppy is an American Shorthair mixed with feral raccoon.</p>
